      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=nc959bne25]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=nc959bne25]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=gk2ngd14ql]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=gk2ngd14ql]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=y5y5mppfbv]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=y5y5mppfbv]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=bvi6w8nbl9]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=bvi6w8nbl9]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=tmamp3956c]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=tmamp3956c]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=tueu5v8xxe]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=tueu5v8xxe]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=uz3whgqz7p]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=uz3whgqz7p]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=q9qsppgq6z]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=q9qsppgq6z]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=d0pq0jt5iu]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=d0pq0jt5iu]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ocn3l0cq90]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ocn3l0cq90]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=wibh6o2sqd]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=wibh6o2sqd]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ohc8se0jhz]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ohc8se0jhz]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=my93jrhk3g]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=my93jrhk3g]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=neeo2yyhtj]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=neeo2yyhtj]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RU_ProjectMonitor_header.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145995/RU_ProjectMonitor_header.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762498268676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/600145995/RU_ProjectMonitor_header.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762498268676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"654901264\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RU_ProjectMonitor_header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"600145995\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"b3d53a7f-830e-4ef8-8e7b-2a01c7f9438f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145995/RU_ProjectMonitor_header.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762498268676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145995/RU_ProjectMonitor_header.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762498268676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><h1 id=\"Projects-RenderManProjectBasedLearning\"><span data-colorid=\"tmamp3956c\">RenderMan Project Based Learning</span></h1><p>Ever wanted to know how RenderMan and Pixar artists create their inspiring imagery?  </p><p>Well, you&rsquo;re in luck &hellip; here&rsquo;s a wide variety of projects to help you understand every aspect of how each image was made, complete with downloadable scenes for you to inspect, pick apart, and learn from.</p><hr /><h1 id=\"Projects-FeaturedProject\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"tueu5v8xxe\">Featured Project</span></strong></h1><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/562823215/The+Hunted\" data-linked-resource-id=\"562823215\" data-linked-resource-version=\"34\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"thehunted_header.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145995/thehunted_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762681496531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/600145995/thehunted_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762681496531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"541\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657162917\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"thehunted_header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"600145995\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"5fec994c-eefd-424d-af2c-6f5b689012ec\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145995/thehunted_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762681496531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=428 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145995/thehunted_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762681496531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ocn3l0cq90\">Project</span></strong>:  The Hunted<br />RenderMan Art Challenge Hero Image</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ohc8se0jhz\">Created &amp; Written by</span></strong>: Eugene Riecansky</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Night sets across the land as the UFO-hunting van is out in the wilderness, looking and searching for his ultimate prize &hellip; to finally spot a UFO. </p><p>What started like every other night takes an unexpected turn &hellip; the UFO hunter becomes the hunted as an unseen UFO appears out of the darkness and snaps him up in its tractor beam.</p><hr /><h1 id=\"Projects-Projects\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"my93jrhk3g\">Projects</span></strong></h1></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/562823215/The+Hunted\" data-linked-resource-id=\"562823215\" data-linked-resource-version=\"34\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"thehunted.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145995/thehunted.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504008003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/600145995/thehunted.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504008003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"655097881\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"thehunted.jpg\" data-base-url=