man.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145995/f1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504008103&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"neeo2yyhtj\">Making an F1 Car</span></strong></p><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/604438600/Stirling+VFX\" data-linked-resource-id=\"604438600\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"stirloing.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145995/stirloing.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504008136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/600145995/stirloing.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504008136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"655097905\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"stirloing.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"600145995\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"a6ad3690-df9d-408f-910e-aa115e3ebfb8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145995/stirloing.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504008136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145995/stirloing.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762504008136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;heig